# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
# BRERC Public Dashboard — .gitignore
#
# GOVERNANCE-CRITICAL. The provided BRERC record subset is REAL CLIENT DATA and
# must never be committed (Data_Governance_and_Compliance.md §6). Secrets must
# never be committed (§6). Do not remove the `data/` or `.env` rules below.
# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------

# --- Real client data: NEVER COMMIT ----------------------------------------
# All local datasets live under data/ which is ignored wholesale. Only the
# synthetic demo seed under db/seed/ (clearly labelled) is version-controlled.
data/
*.gpkg
*.shp
*.shx
*.dbf
*.prj
# CSV/Parquet exports are ignored by default to avoid accidental client-data
# commits. The one allow-listed exception is the synthetic demo file.
*.csv
*.parquet
!db/seed/*.csv
!web/**/*.csv

# --- Secrets: NEVER COMMIT --------------------------------------------------
.env
.env.*
!.env.example
*.pem
*.key
secrets/

# --- Python -----------------------------------------------------------------
__pycache__/
*.py[cod]
*.egg-info/
.eggs/
.pytest_cache/
.mypy_cache/
.ruff_cache/
.venv/
venv/
htmlcov/
.coverage
.coverage.*

# --- Node / web -------------------------------------------------------------
node_modules/
web/dist/
web/coverage/
*.tsbuildinfo
.eslintcache

# --- Build / tooling --------------------------------------------------------
dist/
build/
.cache/
*.log

# --- OS / editor ------------------------------------------------------------
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
.idea/
.vscode/*
!.vscode/extensions.json
!.vscode/settings.json.example
